    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The CFD model is judged credible for the stated COU: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device and supporting a 510(k) substantial equivalence determination via relative hemolysis index comparison. The assessment team notes that the model influence is medium (device testing will confirm results), which is consistent with the MRL 2 designation and the medium assurance level of this package.",
